  "text": "For the two-dimensional Kelvin-Helmholtz problem, the motion is completely driven by the (regularized) initial condition [CITATION_1] . Using standard arguments (taking the curl), for the vorticity \u03c9 = \u2207 \u00d7 u (scalar-valued in 2D), problem (1) transforms to",
